<doc id="909292" wikidata="Q6261711" url="?curid=909292" title="John Valder">
<text>John Valder (21 September 1931 – 9 May 2017) was an Australian politician who was president of the federal Liberal Party of Australia and chairman of the Australian Stock Exchange.

Valder was a founding member of the &#x27;Not happy, John!&#x27; campaign.

==References==
